  "comments": "<p>The first number in serial number is the last number in year.<br>E.g.:<br>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Serial number: <strong>7</strong>840534962 = 200<strong>7</strong><br>&nbsp;</li><li>Serial number: <strong>8</strong>471640025 = 200<strong>8</strong><br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br><i>Remember to <u>check signatures</u> as a \"7\" can indicate <u>both</u> 1997 and 2007!</i><br><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63d9f47147da9.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63d9f47147da9.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P63; signatures Kjell-Olof Feldt &amp; Urban Bäckström (1997-1998)<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63d9f50a0f0c1.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63d9f50a0f0c1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P63; signatures Sven Hulterström &amp; Urban Bäckström (1999-2002)<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63d9f57969f05.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63d9f57969f05.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P63; signatures Jan Bergqvist &amp; Lars Heikensten (2003-2005)<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63d9f5d3e0345.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63d9f5d3e0345.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P63; signatures Jan Bergqvist &amp; Stefan Ingves (2006)<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63d9f61362986.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63d9f61362986.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P63; signatures Johan Gernandt &amp; Stefan Ingves (2007-2014)</p>",
